headline: Autodesk CEO explains software maker's role in AI build-out
summary: Autodesk (ADSK) president and CEO, Andrew Anagnost, sits down with Market Catalysts host Julie Hyman to discuss the ongoing industrial boom's role in building out artificial intelligence (AI) infrastructure. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.

headline: How Is Autodesk's Stock Performance Compared to Other Software Stocks?
summary: Autodesk has notably outperformed other software stocks over the past year, and analysts remain strongly bullish on the stock’s prospects.
